value.0: Long dead, this tree appears to have been burnt and scarred. There are symbols written in blood and obscene runes carved into its broken trunk.

This ancient looking stone is covered in lichen and marks from travelers long since past and dead. Still, engraved much deeper than anyone can defile is the name of the road the person is traveling upon...
This bit of foliage may have something concealed underneath...

Value.value: This area feels...wrong. It is as though a thousand eyes have opened at once and are staring at you. The woods no longer feel safe...And the source is the dead tree in the center of this grove.
